</p>
<p>The biggest thing we need to change is the <code>$env</code> and <code>$debug</code> variables. Let's grab
that code from <code>index.php</code>. PhpStorm is being weird and hiding my <code>web/</code> directory...
now it's back. Copy the 4 dotenv lines from <code>index.php</code>. Now in <code>console</code>, delete
the <code>$env</code> and <code>$debug</code> lines and paste our stuff:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="42dd0c174f">
